<p>Dear [FIRST_NAME]</p>
<p>This email confirms your appointment with Dr Alex Fois on [APPOINTMENT_DATE] at [APPOINTMENT_TIME] at the Woolcock Clinic.</p>
<p>IMPORTANT:</p>
<p>You will receive a confirmation SMS 72 hours before your appointment. To secure your appointment you must SMS &lsquo;Yes&rdquo; to confirm your attendance.</p>
<p>When a patient cancels their appointment or does not attend without giving notice, they prevent another patient from being seen.&nbsp; Therefore, your Doctor requires a 48-hour cancellation notice for any appointment changes.</p>
<p>A charge of $100 will apply for any appointment changes that may occur without appropriate notice.&nbsp;</p>
<p><u>What to bring</u>:</p>
<ol>
<li>A Valid Referral &ndash; Indefinite referrals will not be accepted.</li>
<li>Your Medicare/DVA card/Pension card</li>
<li>Any test results (for example, blood tests, X-rays, scans)</li>
<li>A medication list or medications</li>
<li>An acquaintance form, <em>please find attached or arrive fifteen minutes early and complete at the clinic.</em></li>
<li>During the COVID Crisis please ensure that you wear a mask at the clinic. This will help to ensure the safety and wellbeing of yourself and everyone you come in contact with at the clinic.</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Screening for COVID 19</strong></p>
<p>Please&nbsp;<strong>do not attend&nbsp;</strong>your appointment if:</p>
<ul>
<li>You have been diagnosed with COVID-19</li>
<li>You have had any of the following&nbsp;<a href="https://www.health.nsw.gov.au/Infectious/covid-19/Pages/frequently-asked-questions.aspx#1-4">symptomsâ€‹</a>&nbsp;in the last 14 days:&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
<ul>
<li>fever (37.5&deg; or higher)</li>
<li>cough</li>
<li>sore throat</li>
<li>shortness of breath (difficulty breathing)</li>
<li>runny nose</li>
<li>loss of taste</li>
<li>loss of smell.</li>
</ul>
<li>You have developed any other respiratory symptoms</li>
<li>You have been a contact of someone diagnosed with COVID-19</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><u>Payment for your consultation:</u></strong></p>
<p>The consultation fee for your first visit will be $460.00&nbsp; (rebate $234.85).&nbsp; If other services are required on the day, additional fees are payable. We accept EFTPOS, credit cards, but no cash or cheques.</p>
<p>All subsequent consultations will also attract a fee of approximately $250. (rebate ranging between $67.80 and $118.65) <strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>
<p>We are able to submit your claim to Medicare on site, given we have a valid referral and Medicare details.</p>
<p>Please note that this is a private clinic and Dr Fois doesn&rsquo;t Bulk Bill as a standard rule.</p>
<p>We look forward to welcoming you at the Woolcock Clinic and wish you all the best for your visit.</p>
